msgid ""
"ARE YOU SURE YOU WANT TO CHANGE THE UNDERVOLT VALUE? IF YES, SYSTEM WILL "
"REBOOT AFTER THE CHANGE.  THIS CAN ALSO LEAD TO FAIL BOOTING OF YOUR "
"DEVICE.  THIS CAN BE REVERTED BUT WILL REQUIRE ACCESS TO A COMPUTER WITH A "
"SD CARD READER TO DO SO."
msgstr ""
"CZY NA PEWNO CHCESZ ZMIENIĆ TĄ WARTOŚĆ UNDERVOLTOWANIA? JEŚLI TAK SYSTEM "
"URUCHOMI SIĘ PONOWNIE PO TEJ ZMIANIE. TO MOŻE SPOWODOWAĆ NIEPOWODZENIE W "
"PONOWNYM URUCHOMIENIU URZĄDZENIA. MOŻE TO ZOSTAĆ ODWRÓCONE ALE WYMAGA TO "
"DOSTĘPU DO KOMPUTERA Z CZYTNIKIEM KART SD."

msgid ""
"IF SYSTEM FAILS TO BOOT, JUST REMOVE THE .UNDERVOLT.LIGHT FROM THE END OF "
"THE FDT /rk3566-OC.dtb line in the EXTLINUX.CONF TEXT FILE LOCATED IN YOUR "
"FAT32 BOOT PARTITION IN THE EXTLINUX FOLDER TO REVERT TO THE STOCK CPU "
"VOLTAGE SETTINGS."
